 SUV。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-05/a6662970-ffb5-11ed-bff0-94e24e176cc0" style="height:1280px;width:1920px;" alt="Range Rover SV Edition 一个 BASS 座椅" data-uuid="b2727037-8873-3f0a-bdd5-c500ce23d9ce"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">捷豹路虎</div></figure><p>Range Rover Sport SV Edition One 第一年已经售罄。您可以<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.landroverusa.com/range-rover/range-rover-sport/sv.html">注册</a>以接收有关其他 SV 调整级别的通知，并且有迹象表明 BASS 将在未来得到更广泛的应用。</p><p>不管这个座位有多好，它只是 Subpac 的开始。该公司一直在向电影院、音乐制作人、VR 模拟创作者和游戏玩家推销其触觉和骨传导的组合，并拥有一个可以为座椅和可穿戴设备带来振动的 Flow 平台（想想<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2017-01-06-the-basslet-puts-a-haptic-subwoofer-on-your-wrist.html">Lofelt 的 Basslet</a>之类的东西）。该公司还希望进军航空和整体健康领域。如果触觉音频进入您购买和使用的更多设备，请不要感到惊讶，即使它仅限于高端产品。</p><p></p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/range-rovers-next-luxury-add-on-a-car-seat-that-vibrates-to-music-141725247.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/range-rovers-next-luxury-add-on-a-car-seat-that-vibrates-to-music-141725247.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 8f7886f5-a3fd-4a11-a259-89919395dae8</guid><dc:creator>乔恩·芬加斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Wed, 31 May 2023 14:17:25 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1685542647</ingested><modified> 2023-05-31T14:17:31+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jon Fingas]]></category><media:content height="1280" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-05/ac56f3a0-ffb0-11ed-8fbf-40d2b60ce4fb" width="1920"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![